    "如果您之前在其他设备上购买过订阅,可以通过点击下方的\"恢复购买\"按钮来恢复您的订阅。请确保您使用的是购买时所用的Apple ID 账号。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "If you have previously purchased a subscription on another device, you can restore your subscription by clicking the \"Restore Purchase\" button below. Please ensure that you are using the Apple ID account you used when purchasing."
